name: B._Roundtree
text:
B. Roundtree
B. Roundtree was a nurse at Calhoun Memorial Hospital in March 1989.
As Roundtree tended to patient Annie Blackburn, who spoke a message about being with "Laura" and "Dale" and that the "good" Dale was trapped in "the Lodge." Roundtree did not respond, but noticed that Annie was in a catatonic state. The nurse took a ring from Annie's hand and put it on her own.
She marveled at it in the mirror before leaving the room.
